Package: proximalr
Type: Package
Title: proimalr: A Comprehensive and Elegant Choice for Proximal Causal Inference
Version: 0.0.0001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ruizhe", "Deng", email = "drizmiz@outlook.com", role = c("cre", "com")),
    person("Xu", "Shi", email = "shixu@umich.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: A comprehensive and user-friendly package 
    for proximal causal inference methods,
    i.e. those from all negative control and proximal causal inference papers. 
    You will no longer need to bother with any inconsistency 
    of the interfaces of current codes. 
